<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ur">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Sunnaten Mubarak</title>

<style>
body {
    background: black;
    color: white;
    font-family: Arial;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

/* Animation Background */
body::before {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, green, black, green);
    background-size: 400% 400%;
    animation: bgAnimation 10s infinite;
    z-index: -1;
}

@keyframes bgAnimation {
    0% {background-position: 0% 50%;}
    50% {background-position: 100% 50%;}
    100% {background-position: 0% 50%;}
}

/* Title */
h1 {
    text-align: center;
    color: lime;
    padding: 20px;
}

/* Box Style */
.box {
    border: 1px solid lime;
    margin: 15px;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
}

/* Image Placeholder */
.image {
    border: 2px dashed white;
    height: 150px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 10px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<h1>نبی پاک ﷺ کی سنتیں مبارک ✨</h1>
<p style="text-align:center; color: lightgreen;">
ان پر عمل کریں اور دوسروں کو بھی بتائیں ❤️
</p>

<div class="box">
<p>1️⃣ مسواک کرنا 🙂</p>
<div class="image">Image</div>
</div>

